gnome-paint (0.3+bzr73-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * New bzr snapshot build:
    - src/cv_rect_select.c: update rect select code
    - src/color.c, src/cv_airbrush_tool.h, src/cv_color_pick_tool.h,
      src/cv_curve_tool.h, src/cv_ellipse_tool.h, src/gp_point_array.c,
      src/main.c, src/undo.c: cleaned warning message
    - src/cv_flood_fill_tool.c, src/pixbuf_util.c, src/pixbuf_util.h: 
        Adds undo for flood fill
    - src/selection.c, src/selection.h, src/common.h, src/undo.c,
      src/cv_rect_select.c, src/cv_resize.c, src/cv_resize.h,
      src/gp-image.c, src/gp-image.h:
        added first version of selection area with move and resize. 
    - src/cv_eraser_tool.c, src/cv_eraser_tool.h, src/color.c,
      src/cv_drawing.c, src/main.c: Add eraser
    - src/cv_airbrush_tool.c: Adds undo to airbrush. (LP: #592077)
    - data/ui/gnome_paint.ui, src/cv_flood_fill_tool.c, 
      src/cv_rect_select.c, src/pixbuf_util.c, src/pixbuf_util.h,
      src/selection.c, src/selection.h, src/toolbar.c: 
        Fixed pixbuf_util.* for rgba.
    - data/ui/gnome_paint.ui, src/common.h, src/cv_drawing.c,
      src/cv_drawing.h, src/gp-image.c, src/gp-image.h, src/selection.c,
      src/toolbar.c, src/toolbar.h:
        Toggle transparency/opaqeness to selection
    - src/clipboard.c, src/common.h, src/cv_drawing.c, src/main.c,
      src/cv_rect_select.c, src/gp-image.c, src/gp-image.h,
      src/selection.c, src/selection.h, src/toolbar.h, src/undo.c,
      data/ui/gnome_paint.ui:
        Added copy & paste of selection; Added undo of selections;
        Added 'Image' menu; 
        Default size changed to accommodate net-books.
    - po/es_MX.po: add Spanish translation
    - po/ru.po: add Russian translation
    - po/he.po: add Hebrew translation
    - po/zh_CN: add Simplified Chinese translation
    - po/fr.po, po/it.po, po/pt_BR.po: 
        update translations with new translation templates
    - Enable different size/type brushes

  * debian/control:
    - Bump std-ver to 3.9.1
    - Add Vcs-Bzr and Vcs-Browser fields.

